transcript:
I love the idea that if you value a
relationship in your life your
relationship is only as good as the
stories you've lived together and the
memories you've made and if you stop
making stories and memories with people
then you're constantly living in the
past exactly which is so unhealthy it's
and you've seen that in so many
friendships right when you're no longer
creating together you have nothing but
your old memories and after a while that
just dwindles
